action.name: No GeoLocation
action.command: exiv2 -M"del Exif.Image.GPSTag" -M"del Exif.GPSInfo.GPSLatitude" -M"del Exif.GPSInfo.GPSAltitude" -M"del Exif.GPSInfo.GPSLatitudeRef" -M"del Exif.GPSInfo.GPSAltitudeRef" -M"del Exif.GPSInfo.GPSProcessingMethod" -M"del Exif.GPSInfo.GPSLongitudeRef" -M"del Exif.GPSInfo.GPSTimeStamp" -M"del Exif.GPSInfo.GPSDateStamp" -M"del Exif.GPSInfo.GPSLongitude" -M"del Exif.GPSInfo.GPSImgDirection" -M"del Exif.GPSInfo.GPSImgDirectionRef" %N
action.description: Strip all GeoLocation EXIF from Images
